        "name": "Bastion of StoneBuffGrock gains a",
        "type": "Buff | Damage | Shield",
        "description": "Bastion of StoneBuffGrock gains a Shield equal to 10% of his Max HP and empowers the next Basic Attack to deal  Physical Damage equal to 4 (+2% Total Physical Defense)% of the target's Max HP (capped at 300 (+20 × Hero Level) against non-hero units). This effect has a 18-12 seconds cooldown (decreases with level), which reduces by 200% when near terrain.  Grock gains Control Immunity while casting skills and 30 (+4 × Hero Level)% extra Physical Defense while the Shield is active.Skill terms\nPhys",
